data.description: Located in the family-friendly community of Sheldon Ridge, this beautiful home will exceed your expectations. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom property boasts a stone elevation, open floor plan, game room, and a formal dining room. Hone your culinary skills in the chef's kitchen, complete with a tile backsplash, gas range, and breakfast bar. Melt away the stress in the spa-like master suite, featuring dual vanities, a tub, and frameless shower. Nestled between U.S. 90, Sheldon Lake, and Lake Houston, there is no shortage of nearby things to do or places to see for residents. Schools are zoned to Sheldon Independent School District. You don't want to miss this opportunity - call today!
